These are scripts to automatically post updates to the paperbot Twitter 
account [1]. They are meant as a demonstration of things you can do with the
Chronicling America's public API [2].

Install:
- aptitude install wamerican-insane
- pip install -r requirements.pip
- cp config.py.template config.py
- edit credentials in config.py
- ./headline.py
- run it from cron 

